=Introduction=
----

The purposes of this project are:

<ul><li>Design a robotic arm using 3D printable modules.<ul></ul>

</li><li>Build and assemble the arm.<ul></ul>

</li></ul>

<ul><li>Using the Kinect camera, obtain the space position of a person's joints.<ul></ul>

</li><li>Developing, with the previous data, the formules of robotic arm's reverse kinematics.<ul></ul>

</li></ul>

<ul><li>Connect the computer with the Kinect and an Arduino microcontroller that will send the appropiate commands to the servo-motors.<ul></ul>

</li><li>Having fun with our wireless teleoperated robot!  :D<ul></ul>

</li></ul>

