=Development=
----

==General Conception==
<p class="pubdate">Date: <time>2012-03-16</time>

To begin, we have to design the manipulator, which contains the first 4 degrees of freedom, and then the robot end effector, with the other 2 DOF.

<p class="centered"><img src="/uploads/pool__projects_robotic-arm_human_arm_dof.png" alt="/projects/robotic-arm/human_arm_dof.png"/>

The muscles will be servomotors.<p class="centered"><img src="/uploads/pool__projects_robotic-arm_servo.jpg" alt="/projects/robotic-arm/servo.jpg"/>

And for the control, we'll use the Kinect sensor, that allows to get the 3D observed space reconstruction. Of course, using for this Linux.<p class="centered"><img src="/uploads/pool__projects_robotic-arm_kinect_sensor.png" alt="/projects/robotic-arm/kinect_sensor.png"/>

